Class ContainerConfig.SocketConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.avaje.ebean.config.ContainerConfig.SocketConfig
  • Enclosing class:
    ContainerConfig

    public static class ContainerConfig.SocketConfig
extends Object
    Configuration for clustering using TCP sockets.

    This is good for when there are relatively small number of cluster members.
